          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes, both platforms support custom domains on paid plans. Mixo includes custom domain on $9/month plan and up. Durable includes custom domain on $12/month plan and up. Both handle SSL certificates automatically - no technical setup required. Free plans use subdomains (yourname.mixo.io or yourname.durable.co). For professional websites, you'll want the paid plan anyway for custom domain. Neither charges extra for domain connection - it's included in the subscription price."
        }
